    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "A tapping script for Day 15 of the money arc. The script works with the guilt that can surface when you want wealth — the worry that wanting more makes you greedy or selfish, and the belief that desire is a character flaw."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "New to tapping? Read "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works"}}],
            "text": "how EFT tapping works"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " first."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The practice"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 3},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Karate chop"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though part of me feels guilty for wanting more money, I deeply and completely accept myself."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though I sometimes think wealth is selfish, I deeply and completely accept myself."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though I worry people will judge me for wanting financial freedom, I deeply and completely accept myself."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 3},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Tapping round"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Eyebrow:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I've been told that wanting wealth is greedy."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Side of eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Part of me feels guilty just for wanting this."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I worry it means I don't care about others."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under nose:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I fear people will think less of me for wanting more."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Chin:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I've been hiding how much I want."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Collarbone:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I feel torn between desire and guilt."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under arm:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I'm tired of pretending I don't want more."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Top of head:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I'm ready to see this differently."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 3},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Reframe to positive"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Eyebrow:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Wanting wealth is natural and clean."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Side of eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Money lets me help and build and give more."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I can be generous and abundant at the same time."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under nose:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I trust my own values with whatever I have."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Chin:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I deserve financial freedom without apology."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Collarbone:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I welcome wealth as something good."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under arm:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I release the guilt and claim what's mine."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Top of head:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I allow abundance with an open heart."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Tap the round three times, then move to the reframe and tap that three times."}]
      },
      {
